Class Signaling

  • java.lang.Object
    • arcade.agent.module.Signaling
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Module, java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SignalingComplex, SignalingMedium, SignalingRandom, SignalingSimple

    public abstract class Signaling
extends java.lang.Object
implements Module
    Implementation of Module for cell signaling.

    The Signaling module can be used for networks comprising a system of ODEs.
